    "The evaluation result is shown in Table 6.From the result, we can observe that the control method details generate by CataLM are obtain better performance than original LLM.",
    "However, beside the target product and material, the prediction results of the model are also influenced by the category of regulatory methods, which is an input parameter.",
    "This means that for the original LLM and CataLM, the regulatory methods are the same, so the difference in the predicted Faraday effect is not significant.",
    "ConclusionIn this paper, we introduce CataLM, an effective attempt towards catalyst design leveraging the capabilities of large language models.",
    "By undergoing domain pre-training and instruction tuning, our large language model has exhibited robust comprehension and reasoning skills in catalyst knowledge and patterns, achieving advanced performance in application tasks like knowledge extraction and recommendation of control methods."
